	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='na tāvāyaṃ paribhāsi'}}
paripucchatāya pañhāya atiyanaṃ ekassa kiñci – ayaṃ vuccate vibhatti hāro.

body.gatha1:
Evaṃetaṃ 
